@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Order flow: wrong items delivered (should verify with replacement-style resolution)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cases/langgraph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue": "My order was delivered with wrong items. I ordered 2 blue shirts but got 1 red shirt and 1 hat.",
  "tenant_id": "shop-acme",
  "app_id": "order-service",
  "time_range": "last_7d"
}

### Order flow: missing item from order (order intent path)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cases/langgraph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue": "One item is missing from my order. I ordered 3 notebooks and only received 2.",
  "tenant_id": "shop-acme",
  "app_id": "order-service",
  "time_range": "last_7d"
}

### Order flow: ambiguous package issue (should ask clarification)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cases/langgraph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue": "I received something weird in my package.",
  "tenant_id": "shop-acme",
  "app_id": "order-service",
  "time_range": "last_7d"
}

### Order flow: SKU mismatch phrasing (order classification signal check)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cases/langgraph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue": "Order SKU mismatch: expected blue-shirt-XL, got hat-red-M.",
  "tenant_id": "shop-acme",
  "app_id": "order-service",
  "time_range": "last_24h"
}

### Contrast case: login failure (non-order path)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cases/langgraph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue": "Users cannot log in during traffic spikes.",
  "tenant_id": "tenant-acme",
  "app_id": "billing-portal",
  "time_range": "last_24h"
}

### Validation case: missing required field (expect 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cases/langgraph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue": "My order has wrong items.",
  "tenant_id": "shop-acme",
  "time_range": "last_24h"
}
